Metrics Decision Matrix by Use Case. Table with 5 Use Cases as rows: Customer Support Chatbot, Code Generation, Summarization, RAG System, Agent System. Three priority columns: Primary Metric, Secondary Metric, Guardrail. Values: Support: Accuracy / P95 Latency <2s / Hallucinations. Code: Functional Correctness / Speed / Security. Summary: Faithfulness / Coverage / PII Leak. RAG: Hit-Rate / Faithfulness / MRR. Agent: Success Rate / Step Efficiency / Cost/Task. Color-coded cells, German labels.